\ce{SiO2 + 6NaF + 6HCl -> H2SiF6 + 6NaCl + 2H2O}

Notice that the \ce{6HF}, \ce{6NaOH}, and \ce{6H2O} cancel out, leaving us with our target reaction.

**4. Calculate the Overall Enthalpy Change:**

